ygData.messageBody:
I am a gnome necro and am barely tolerated by neriak. But i havnt worked on
my faction there much as the halfling camps you have to take can be rough.
(dont even take the green camp by yourself) i can get on the first 2 levels
but the main level where the necro guild is I am KOS. Go figure.
